         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">November 24 [186]4 ¶ editorial addition. ¶ Sir ¶  ¶ I regret extremely to learn from Mr Heyne ¶ Ernst HeynewasM's clerical assistant. ¶  ¶ this morning that you consider that I have been guilty of ins...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">64.11.24c</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From George Sprigg</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">No. 64/653, unit 4, pp. 132-4, VPRS 2225 outward letterpress copy books, Acclimatisation Society of Victoria, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">November 24 [186]4<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">editorial addition.</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I regret extremely to learn from Mr Heyne<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ernst Heyne<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>was<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>M's clerical assistant.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>this morning that you consider that I have been guilty of insulting you. If<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; ">RH: By? something wrong or missing?</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>my conduct in reference to the swans in stating that they have been hawked about for sale. As I feel sure that this impression is only in consequence of a misunderstanding I would respectfully venture to lay before you the circumstances of the case. Some time ago Mr Brascher<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn3" n="4">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Not further identified.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>who generally acts as Mr McKay's town agent called on me and asked whether the society<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn4" n="5">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Acclimatisation Society of Victoria.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>would purchase some black swans saying he had some<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>for sale in Westernport for 30/-<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>per pair, I told him that some were required but that the Council<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn5" n="6">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The Council of the Acclimatisation Society of Victoria.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>would only give 20/-<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>per pair, he answered he would write &amp; ask whether they would take that price. Subsequently he (&amp; his sons) called again and said the swans could not be had for less than<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>30/-. When I got your letter<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn6" n="7">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; ">Letter not found.?</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>about the birds<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn7" n="8">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; ">is this M writing as director of the gardens, or on behalf of the Trustees of the Royal Park?</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>and<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn8" n="9">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; ">RH: word missing?</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>the Council had authorised the purchase I called on Mr Brascher<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn9" n="10">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; ">RH: word missing?</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>told<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>him you were going to offer 20/-<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>per pair but that the swans must be sent up directly. Since then the swans have been offered to me by<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>a third person at 25/-<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>per pair but I declined to purchase.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Now we come to the transaction of yesterday. I met Mr McKay in the […]<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn10" n="11">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">illegible.</seg>
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="2"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; ">RH: street?</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>[accompanied by some messengers] he gave me your letters and I then said that swans ought to have been up before, and that I could not pay him until the Council met on Tuesday. A person who I believe is his wife came up at the time and in a very rude and angry manner told him not stand there talking to me but to go back at once to you and I then declined to have any thing more to say on the matter. Being on my way to Mr Sumner (who had sent for me) I did not think it necessary to turn back to write a letter but asked your messenger to explain the matter to you as he had been a witness to the whole affair.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The reason why I could not pay Mr McKay is that as there was no quorum on Tuesday no cheques were signed and I have no funds whatever on hand nor shall I have [until] after the meeting on Tuesday next<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I never for one moment thought of refusing to take the swans if you had definitely taken charge of them for the Society but having had large dealing with Mr Brascher I have never yet had any difficulty about payment.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Mr Heyne informs me that you consider it a gross insult not replying to your letter by writing but this I trust you will […]<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn11" n="12">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">illegible.</seg>
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="2"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; ">RH: recohnise? realise?</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>it was impossible to do on the […]<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn12" n="13">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">illegible.</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>[strict]<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn13" n="14">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; ">RH: street?</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>and I [supposed] that the messenger would […]<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn14" n="15">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">two illegible words.</seg>
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="2"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; ">RH: report?</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>what took place. Being very [unwell] and extremely busy all day the whole matter had escaped my memory until I saw Mr Heyne this morning.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>It is the first time in my life that such a charge has been made against me and I can only express my sincere regret that it would be […]<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn15" n="16">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">two illegible words.</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>now and beg that you will accept my most humble apologies if you […]<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn16" n="17">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">illegible.</seg>
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="2"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; ">RH: feel? believe?</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>that I have in any way unintentionally offended you.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I am</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sir</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your most Obedt Servant</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Geo Sprigg</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">To Dr Mueller F.R.S.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Vice President of Acclimatisation Society<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn17" n="18">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; ">anything in minutes?</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
         </div>
      </body>
